                                                ---| MANAGEMENT SERVICES (System V) | ---

-| Configuration file:
# vi /etc/inittab

-| Directory Scripts:
# /etc/init.d/*
# /etc/rc[1,2,3,4,5,6].d/

-| Reboot:
# init 6

-| Shutdown:
# init 0

-| Verify service:
# service <service_name> status

-| Management service:
# service <service_name> stop | start| restart 

-| Enable/Disable service:
# chkconfig <service_name> on | off

-| Show Runlevel:
# runlevel

-| Turn off SO:
# shutdown -h now
# halt


                                                ---| MANAGEMENT SERVICES (System D) | ---

-| Verify services:
# systemctl list-units

-| Verify service:
# systemctl status <service_name>

-| Management service:
# systemctl stop | start| restart | reload <service_name>

-| Enable/Disable service:
# systemctl enable | disable| <service_name>

-| Verifiy if the service is enabled:
# systemctl is-enabled <service_name>

-| Show Runlevel:
# systemctl get-default

